title: Hour 2 - Doug Gottlieb (05-21-20)

description:
Doug Gottlieb debates with Dan on the NBA top 5 and top 10 players. Doug disagrees with Dan on his stance about Kareem Abdul-Jabbar. Doug eventually admits that Lebron James is a top 5 player.
